# Title: Okta Application Modified or Deleted
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-09-12
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when an application is modified or deleted.
# MITRE Tactic: Impact
# Tags: attack.impact
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/identity/okta/okta_application_modified_or_deleted.yml

eventType IN ("application.lifecycle.update", "application.lifecycle.delete")